<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_178_r1l15"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft ʒu VVermberg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l16">vıcʒtum Jn Nider payern </ab>
</div>
