<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum als <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_178_r1l17"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
</ab></add> wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt / daʒ vns
                        VVeinmar Eker </ab>
