                                <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / vvıe er ſıch vor vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l20">hab <expan>müſſe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>entſıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> von eins angrıffs
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . den vns frıdel
                            <expan>niema<ex>n</ex>tſ</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l21">gnoſʒ vnd ſein <expan>geſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> getan
                                <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daran er kein ſchulde gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l22">hab . des ſey er ʒu <expan>groſſ<ex>em</ex></expan>
                        ſchaden <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Darauf wır Jm deſmals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l23"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ wır Jm keins
                            <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> nie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l24">gewartt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch hınfür
                        keins <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l25">vnd <expan>weſt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt Jm
