                                <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l27"><expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> er ſchraib vns / vvıe
                        wır Jn gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>rſchaft</expan> von payern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l28"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>klagt</expan>
<expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . des er ʒu <expan>ſchade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . Vnd <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l29"><expan>fürcʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> /
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> er wölt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        vnd der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> veynd ſein Darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l30">wır Jm do <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_178_r1l31"><expan>weſte<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ wır Jn
                                <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> verklagt
